title: Question regarding the PES kcet counselling on 5th/12th July
content:
So for the counselling on 7th June (through    j e e),only the top 5000 rankers were called .

Will it be the same with the kcet merit list?
What rankers will be eligible for the counselling?

I've got 4123 in the PES kcet merit list ranking , and wanted to know,will I be eligible for the counselling on 5th/12th July ? And if I am,do i have a chance to get ECE in e city campus ?

comments.body: None of your questions can be answered by anyone here. As you may not know, this is the first time PES is holding its own KCET based admissions. Nobody knows anything about this process.
